  <summary date="2021-04-06T20:58:28Z" status="Introduced in House">Food Allergy Safety, Treatment, Education, and Research Act of 2021 or the FASTER Act of 2021

This bill expands&#160;the definition of major food allergen for purposes of certain food-labeling requirements&#160;to specifically include sesame. In addition, the Department of Health and Human Services must report on certain information related to food allergy research and data collection activities.</summary>
